</a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>/<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b>:\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a>, led by <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a><br />\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Manderly.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Manderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/20px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/30px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/40px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a></li></ul></li></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Sunderland.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Sunderland.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/20px-House_Sunderland.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/30px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Sunderland.svg/40px-House_Sunderland.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Marla_Sunderland\" title=\"Marla Sunderland\">Marla Sunderland</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Targaryen.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/20px-House_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/30px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/1e/House_Targaryen.svg/40px-House_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Stark.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Stark.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/20px-House_Stark.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/30px-House_Stark.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7e/House_Stark.svg/40px-House_Stark.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Stark\" title=\"Torrhen Stark\">Torrhen Stark</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/File:House_Manderly.svg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"House Manderly.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/20px-House_Manderly.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/30px-House_Manderly.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/House_Manderly.svg/40px-House_Manderly.svg.png 2x\" /></a>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Warrick_Manderly\" title=\"Warrick Manderly\">Warrick Manderly</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Strength</td></tr><tr><td></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\">Houses of the North<br /><a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavosi</a> galleys</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Sistermen's Rebellion</b> was a failed uprising of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a> against the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Wars_of_Conquest\" title=\"Wars of Conquest\">Wars of Conquest</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sistermen%27s_Rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon%27s_Landing\" title=\"Aegon&#39;s Landing\">Aegon's Landing</a> and the coronation of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Aegonfort\" title=\"Aegonfort\">Aegonfort</a> threw the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">Seven Kingdoms</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> into disarray. Aegon's sister, Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Visenya_Targaryen\" title=\"Visenya Targaryen\">Visenya Targaryen</a>, destroyed the fleet of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_Mountain_and_Vale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of Mountain and Vale\">Kings of Mountain and Vale</a>, during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_in_the_waters_off_Gulltown\" title=\"Battle in the waters off Gulltown\">battle in the waters off Gulltown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The lords of the <a href=\"/index.php/Three_Sisters\" title=\"Three Sisters\">Three Sisters</a>, who had sworn allegiance to the Arryns centuries earlier in the <a href=\"/index.php/War_Across_the_Water\" title=\"War Across the Water\">War Across the Water</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> renounced King <a href=\"/index.php/Ronnel_Arryn_(king)\" title=\"Ronnel Arryn (king)\">Ronnel Arryn</a> and named <a href=\"/index.php/Marla_Sunderland\" title=\"Marla Sunderland\">Marla Sunderland</a> as queen.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> The Arryns eventually submitted to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a> when Visenya landed with <a href=\"/index.php/Vhagar\" title=\"Vhagar\">Vhagar</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>, with Ronnel becoming the <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_East\" title=\"Warden of the East\">Warden of the East</a> for King Aegon.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>After being anointed by the <a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aegon%27s_Conquest)\" title=\"High Septon (Aegon&#39;s Conquest)\">High Septon</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>, Aegon ordered Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen_Stark\" title=\"Torrhen Stark\">Torrhen Stark</a>, his new <a href=\"/index.php/Warden_of_the_North\" title=\"Warden of the North\">Warden of the North</a>, to end the Sistermen's Rebellion. Since the Arryn fleet had not yet been rebuilt after Gulltown, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Warrick_Manderly\" title=\"Warrick Manderly\">Warrick Manderly</a> led the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> army to the <a href=\"/index.php/Bite\" title=\"Bite\">Bite</a> on galleys hired from <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Sistermen\" title=\"Sistermen\">Sistermen</a> surrendered instead of fighting when they saw Warrick's fleet and Visenya on her <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragon</a>. They deposed Marla for her younger brother, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Steffon_Sunderland\" title=\"Steffon Sunderland\">Steffon Sunderland</a>, who yielded the Three Sisters to the Targaryens and Arryns.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manderly\" title=\"House Manderly\">House Manderly</a> took one of Steffon's sons as a hostage, while House Arryn took the other. After five years of imprisoned exile, Marla had her tongue removed and joined the <a href=\"/index.php/Silent_sisters\" title=\"Silent sisters\">silent sisters</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sistermen%27s_Rebellion&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_reign_of_the_dragons:_the_conquest.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Reign of the Dragons: The Conquest.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_vale.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Vale.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Reign of the Dragon - The Wars of King Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2